Most of the resources returned the API follow the HATEOS approach: they will tell you what else you can do to them.
HATEOS in this API follows this general pattern

```json
{
    "content": { ... the resource data ...},
    "links": [
        {
            "rel": "a_description_of_what_happens_at_this_uri",
           "href": "the_herf_that_gives_the_above_resource"
         },
         ... more rels/hrefs ...
    ]
}
```
